Delete
--------
Delete means we can delete only record not the table  & in delete we can use WHERE CLAUSE also for delete 
syntax: DELETE FROM EMPLOYEES WHERE EMP_ID=12;

TURCATE
----------
Turcate means we can delete all the record at a time we can't delete one record  AND  here we can't use where clause
syntax: TURNCATE TABLE EMPLOYEES;

Drop
------
Drop means it will delete table  and record as well 
syntax: DROP TABLE EMPLOYEES;
